{"tid":2017400,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】馬來西亞網紅糖糖被批過份賣弄　靠一招IG粉絲突破100萬","createTime":"2020-05-15T05:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T11:55:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2be70e014efe76b769f5ca94de4d964cb244c3","tid":2017400,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:36:12.000Z","msg":"網紅風氣盛行，基本上只要有一部手機，有一個IG帳戶，再加過萬追蹤者就可以自稱「網紅」，不過要有過萬甚至過百萬粉絲，就完成是另一種境界了。早前曾經同大家介紹過馬來西亞的IG美女Pui Yi糖糖，經常被網民批評賣弄身材，但就似乎越鬧越紅，最後更索性自資出性感寫真賺錢。這位大馬網紅Pui Yi糖糖，在短短兩個月內IG追蹤者人數就由80萬急升到104萬，今日（14/5）還獲得Instagram「加持」給予藍剔認證，認真厲害。"},{"pid":"71a4888a1bc2ade60511fe21af74308eb042f02c","tid":2017400,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4488089/org/eca734ebe97123476a94991beca0e12a.jpg/MK7OrdIwvbcNVJf2ZuydBs9LhGyVAC4DDYxhlw2MYZc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4488089%2Forg%2Feca734ebe97123476a94991beca0e12a.jpg%2FMK7OrdIwvbcNVJf2ZuydBs9LhGyVAC4DDYxhlw2MYZc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=b1fb9b4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b297ba1e8ecb9fa301124cae76c4ae656add99e","tid":2017400,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4488121/org/23a568a1af90718bcae24cb75caae7e7.jpg/pxdShTQW8_Bc93T1XJDGBMw8Qd6uPiE1FGtogxRraIM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4488121%2Forg%2F23a568a1af90718bcae24cb75caae7e7.jpg%2FpxdShTQW8_Bc93T1XJDGBMw8Qd6uPiE1FGtogxRraIM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=843b05db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬來西亞的糖糖擁有傲人身材。（IG@ms_puiyi）"},{"pid":"9424a29c6cce4f3641b4b203d32dace5ccc0a715","tid":2017400,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4488128/org/7a8c6b79306c70e9e4b3